lead_paragraph: Hillary Clinton, a likely U.S. presidential candidate, is urging the world to take action and address "the great unfinished business of the 21st century" — the achievement of equality for women that 189 nations called for at a groundbreaking U.N. conference 20 years ago.

headline.main: Hillary Clinton Urges Action to Achieve Women's Equality
